data.description: Renovated in 2020, this spacious  brick ranch  is a MUST SHOW!!  Situated on a large lot  in a convenient downtown neighborhood, it is possibly the best buy in Walterboro. It won't stay on the market long.To fully appreciate all the upgrades, you need to view this home in person.  As you enter you are greeted by striking updated flooring which is present throughout the house.  There is both a living room and a family room, both with fireplaces. The eat-in kitchen features stainless appliances & new white shaker cabinets. Both baths were also updated with new fixtures & hardware.. Even the hot water heater is new.  The bedrooms are nice sized.  The master has 2 closets & attached bath. The landscaping is just begging for a green thumb owner to add curb appeal. Schedule a showing.TODAY!
